body:
Hi, I'm a spanish YouTuber and I have 8k suscribers, I would like to know if is there is a YouTuber or famous rank, because I'm going to upload some videos on the server.

I asked a mod and he told me about a media rank, or something like that but I didn't understand, could you explain me about that rank? 

My YT channel: http://youtube.com/user/InacheteHD
 
May I get one of these ranks because of my number of subscribers?

Sorry for my bad English, greetings^^

replies.body:
Media rank is when you record/stream Avicus tournaments/Seasons.
To become a "VIP" rank you need 5000 subscribers.
To become a "Youtuber" rank you need 50 000.
You can find out more from here: https://avicus.net/forums/1a60f1fea
 
It may be old but I don't remember anyone updating the rules of the rank, just a bunch of controversies.
